Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.42,0:00:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That must've been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.51,0:00:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Prince Zen and the people\Nat Fort Laxdo were there with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But you did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take the rest of the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone is still worki--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest is important, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll leave first, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki's working hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, I wonder if she knows...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.12,0:00:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,About Prince Izana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Led to an encounter...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahead on the road I've reached...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.93,0:00:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place I have chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where my desires become reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:43.40,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 6: The Back Full of Meaning"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I'll go with Ryu to the herb garden,\Nand then organize the medical records and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shirayuki. Mornin--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:03:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Clarines Kingdom, Wistal Castle,\NApprentice Court Herbalist"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your identification, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They finished making it\Nwhile we were at Fort Laxdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This uniform, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, you also\Nmoved into the castle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I have to work harder\Nand harder from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a ton of studying and work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I'll be busy for a while with the\Nbandit incident and everything at Fort Laxdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We might not be able\Nto see each other for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that make you upset at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Upset? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "How"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya, Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're waiting for the investigation\Nreport from the army for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What about rewriting the\Ncommunication system with the fort?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've sent it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, next--shall we go to the archives?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers at the fort will have\Na hard time of it from now on, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll have them work hard for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To do that, we'll have\Nto prepare the system first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The palace guards are\Nstationed in different places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,\Nthere are a lot of them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear anything about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Zen, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When Master and the\Nothers get busy, I get bored...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The area I'm allowed to be in is limited,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and there are no weapons\Nfor me to clean or repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen, we cannot\Nallow you to proceed further.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki, Mitsuhide, make yourselves presentable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm to wait until summoned, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Obi, come out! You have ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you like to ask for the unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you will be--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That scratch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this? Just now, there was a sudden--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Prince Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to give this\Nto you as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Obi. Tell me about your scratch later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, uncover your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And stand by in this room. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, the prince is summoning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay. Right away--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come to the Room of Chanting Flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The Room of Chanting Flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Little Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Lord Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide and Kiki are with you, too?\NFriendly, as always, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Why did you\Nhide your return from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:07:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering when you'd notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to know how much you paid\Nattention to what went on around the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please refrain from making any noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you went all the way to Laxdo, Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the report, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It said the soldiers at the fort\Nwere all sick because of the bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't even move. It must've been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he's speaking to Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone with a higher social\Nstatus than the second prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The first prince of Clarines!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You were there with a court herbalist,\Nand another attendant, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't bring him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... he is a newcomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A man with a scratch on his cheek?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he was an outlaw,\Nbut he was yours, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? I didn't see a report about\Nthe punishment of those at the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They were not punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the duty to patrol\Nand protect the surrounding area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,During this incident, they were unable\Nto perform this duty for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They could not be prevented from\Ngoing back to their duties any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Zen, why don't we remove\NLaxdo from your jurisdiction for six months?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it was the bandits' doing,\Nthere was fault in the fort's system.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you will not rebuke the soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,then you will receive the punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A punishment that will make the\Nsoldiers feel even more guilty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be hitting Zen hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're soft on yourself, so you don't want\Nto blame them for something like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Next--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, you all can leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're busy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, we'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go see you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Lord Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide, Kiki. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:10:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, you're Prince Zen's big brother... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a refreshing way to address me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you summon me because of the\NLaxdo incident you spoke of earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why would you ask an outsider like me--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Zen's friend,\Nand a favorite of his, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For Zen, from the royal family,\Nto have a friend and keep her in the castle--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who hears of this would be interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have high hopes, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have something\NZen deems very necessary, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot answer whether or not it is\Nsomething that would be evident to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You are dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't being humble just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,then that means he happily invited a girl with\Nstrange hair from a foreign country into the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's become a good-for-nothing prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Prince Izana\Nsummoned Shirayuki for...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?\NShe called me Zen's big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That was kind of funny, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we finish this up all at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying so soon after arriving?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying this {\i1}because{\i0} I arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Izana went out of his way to\Nsummon you today to deepen your friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it is also important\Nfor your two countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! But why invite just me,\Nnow, after all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Owww...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretending to be sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Clarines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the second prince,\NZen Wisteria. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Well, well.\NI am Raj Schenazade of Tanbarun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I am honored to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought that\NPrince Izana would invite Prince Raj.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he's a\Nscandalous and hopeless prince
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,who wanted to force a\Ntown girl to be his concubine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and then sent her poisoned apples...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a sharp tongue...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was after he summoned\NShirayuki. It bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Zen also said\Nthere must be a reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Izana Wisteria. Welcome, Raj.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we have the chance to meet like this,\Nlet's dispense with the formalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, let us go to the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I got out of guard duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Master and the others\Nhave been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You were born in Tanbarun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen\Nbetween you and Prince Raj?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, that's why I came to get you, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go spy on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? W-Wai--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we can hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen, I hear you have a new attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Haruka. Did my brother say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He is very nimble and skilled.\NAn interesting man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as he is ready to fight when necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot have someone by your side who\Ndoes not pay attention to his surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering what you two talked\Nabout when you went to greet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right. We just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Raj, I heard you\Nhad fallen for a red-haired--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl is in this castle right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... the red-haired...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can at least say her name, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Shirayuki... wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like where this is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the girl left you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you have any lingering affection,\NI can prepare a seat for her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brother, you are\Nreading too much into things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I? It's a good chance, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl might want to go back\Nto her home country, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, their conversation\Nis turning into a bad joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. My break's over,\Nso I have to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I was being told to leave Clarines?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'm not necessary here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Raj.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:17:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you for the offer,\NIzana, but I politely decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki definitely did not leave me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wholeheartedly supported her in\Nher desire to live in another country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I have no lingering affection!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason you cannot see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want your foolish\Nactions to be made public,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,then swear you will never approach\NShirayuki again or say her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I just swore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Zen thinks\Nof Shirayuki as his fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Z-Zen, where...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What he said just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! I had no choice with the\Nway the conversation was going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have exaggerated things a little,\Nbut it's the same thing in the end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The same?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Shirayuki are lovers, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that's not the case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop making a racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then there's no\Nguarantee Shirayuki will not leave you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki knows about the poisoned apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have her somewhere\Nwhere I can keep an eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you will not have her,\Nthen I will welcome Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like that is what\NIzana would prefer, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I would treat her\Nwith courtesy in my castle--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, I'm not done talking--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, Shirayuki is not in this\Ncastle right now to hide what happened that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that there's no guarantee that\NShirayuki will stay with me in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Raj, it's because there's\Nno promise that I wish for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what drives people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Raj and I were not on the same page.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brother. I do not think of Shirayuki\Nas my fiancée, nor have I asked her to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.88,0:20:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Raj...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long he'll be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do if I'm told to\Ngo with him when he leaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say what I could do\Nfor you by your side in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,or why I am here right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's become a good-for-nothing prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have an answer... To any of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The place you decided to go by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I'm in this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see how you live in this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the place where I'll be able to\Ndo that is where I've decided to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I can see you from that place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.05,0:24:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.31,0:24:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, princess? Have you come to dislike it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.35,0:24:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother was always in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.65,0:24:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he's showing his true nature, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.44,0:24:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there will always\Nbe someone on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,0:24:20.15,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 7: Let Me Hear\Nthe Melody of Your Smile"
